				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \overset{\sim }{z} $$\end{document}z~ be an infinitesimal, point-like measurement of the same object.

